{"tid":1984123,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李天命, 黃子華, 梁天琦, sigma - 香港近代哲學史上四大思想家","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T20:52:26.000Z","uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51e10c41962b529b900830cf344c883890ad6dca","tid":1984123,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5v9zxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5v9zxL.png&h=a731bd3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n李天命<br />\n前香港中文大學哲學系講師，以&quot;思方劍&quot;思考藝術聞名於世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FS6HUyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFS6HUyJ.jpg&h=747adec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黃子華<br />\n加拿大阿爾伯塔大學取得哲學學士，棟篤笑帶有哲學成份，教識唔少香港人做人處世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjaBezk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjaBezk.jpg&h=db16ca91&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n梁天琦<br />\n香港大學哲學系畢業，香港人革命先驅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEyK7We.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEyK7We.jpg&h=4bc22f25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nsigma (aka. youtube界呂布)<br />\n台灣某大學某系畢業<br />\n佢唔會攞刀斬你，只會用嚴密既邏輯令你無話可說，唔知點駁<br />\n得罪左佢講聲sor請食飯最明智"},{"pid":"f693de5fffd01586f950bbae76cbf805fdd6a182","tid":1984123,"uid":188011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"其實邊個係sigma?搞乜呢排咁多人提佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829f4a213a99b7f4c3fe13bca4b51531a62db7bd","tid":1984123,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"邏輯學同哲學係兩樣嘢"},{"pid":"1f60859c724f39610c701f5e0358d1a66816a6b2","tid":1984123,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"829f4a213a99b7f4c3fe13bca4b51531a62db7bd","tid":1984123,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T0